# GPRTool -- Project Brief

## What this is
GPRTool is a web-based application for ground penetration radar (GPR) data visualization and analysis, using HTML/CSS/JS with Three.js for 3D rendering. It's deployed on Vercel/GitHub with no npm dependencies. The project includes a LAI (Leaf Area Index) processing pipeline in Python.

