## Current focus
The project is actively working on extracting code from index.html into modular JS files in app/js/ while maintaining compatibility with Chrome (using Edge for development).

## Key constraints
- No Python in app/ directory (LAI pipeline lives in lai/)
- Icons must be inline SVG, never PNG
- Third-party libraries in app/js/lib/ must not be edited
- "Touch it, extract it" rule: extract code from index.html to separate files
- Chrome issues require development in Edge
- No global variables; explicit dependencies only
